grupp03.calculatorApplication.tokens.operators

Class OperatorModule

  • java.lang.Object
    • grupp03.calculatorApplication.tokens.operators.OperatorModule

  • public class OperatorModule
extends java.lang.Object
    Used by the OperatorFactory as a mean to load operator configurations from the operations declaration file. Mainly used as a wrapper for these parsed text declarations.
